Titolo: Elvira: The Arcade Game

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Elvira: The Arcade Game is a side-scrolling platform game released in 1991 for the Amiga, Atari ST, Commodore 64, and MS-DOS by Flair Software. The game is loosely based upon the film Elvira: Mistress of the Dark (film), released in 1988, and she features as the playable character.

